<para><bold>Doxygen Awesome</bold> is a custom CSS theme for Doxygen HTML documentation with many customization options.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1a55803d4667afd0b5d398f378b65f85_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Motivation</title><para>I really like how the Doxygen HTML documentation is structured, but IMHO it looks a bit outdated.</para>
<para>This theme is an attempt to modernize the visuals of Doxygen without changing its overall layout too much.</para>
</sect1>
