<sect1 id="dir_1a55803d4667afd0b5d398f378b65f85_1autotoc_md11">
<title>Browser support</title><para>Tested with</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Chrome 140, Chrome 140 for Android, Chrome 141 for iOS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Safari 26, Safari for iOS 26</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Firefox 143, Firefox 142 for Android, Firefox 143 for iOS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Edge 140</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Opera One 122</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The theme does not strive to be backward compatible with (significantly) older browser versions.</para>
</sect1>
